{"tid":1913343,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"到底支那鎖網可唔可以鎖得全面啲.....","createTime":"2020-03-06T16:51:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T16:53:37.000Z","uid":103653,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"272094a72879069c2aafc1cecbe19177a522408b","tid":1913343,"uid":103653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T16:51:55.000Z","msg":"屌你老母一係就咪撚鎖 一鎖就鎖撚曬佢鎖到變內聯網<br />\n呢掛唔知係咪武漢肺炎搞到個個都唔出街<br />\n留係屋企打機<br />\n廢又唔輸得 <br />\n早一個月玩返Apex 本身都好地地<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點知</span></span><br />\n呢掛啲掛多撚到仆街<br />\n<br />\n你地快啲中武漢肺炎死撚曬佢啦 仆街......<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/03/07/005133_3f6aa14e41e0ec5f61b16a8b2d513127.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F03%2F07%2F005133_3f6aa14e41e0ec5f61b16a8b2d513127.gif&h=a22126db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0bc932d388b00c28ee941440fca9fdbba69ab7c8","tid":1913343,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T16:53:37.000Z","msg":"無<br />\n咁樣領導上唔到pornhub<br />\n<br />\n脫離支那是是香港唯一出路，但絕不能直接獨立，必須先經英美託管一段時間再經公投獨立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1913061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1913061</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n想消滅支那，我們就要帶領支畜暴動和革命，才有機會從內部瓦解支共（輸出革命+加速主義，缺一不可）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1911527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1911527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}